OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fbright evening, but then turning
OL,7,Fcloudy and murky with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain and drizzle developing towards
OL,9,Fmidnight. Rain continuing overnight
OL,10,Fand turning rather breezy. Staying
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FCloud and rain clearing the
OL,14,Fsouth through the morning to leave a
OL,15,Fsunny day for most. Winds falling
OL,16,Flight as the day progresses so a
OL,17,Fpleasant afternoon to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
