OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure building through this period,
OL,7,Fto give plenty of warm sunshine and
OL,8,Flight winds throughout. Perhaps a
OL,9,Flittle more in the way of cloud on
OL,10,FSaturday.
